description:
Ourbloc is a Consulting & Management Company focused on creating a community for helping clients find where their expertise intersects with the emerging blockchain infrastructure. We work with businesses and individuals looking to access the blockchain space. According to The World Trade Organization, Blockchain technology is set to disrupt international trade by adding 3 trillion dollars to the market in 2030. Don't miss out on your piece of the pie!

​Our strongest belief at Ourbloc is data integrity. Protecting the data of our clients comes number one on our list. For that reason, all online client interactions are done on a decentralized private server. All data exchange is also done on a private server.  Don't worry we will provide you with everything you need to get started. Use the form at the bottom of the page to find out more information or sign up for one of our plans by visiting the pricing page.
